---
layout: layout-base.njk
pagination:
  data: stateSummariesUS
  size: 1
  alias: state
permalink: "/planting-dates/states/{{ state.key }}/index.html"
---

<header class="header">
  <h1>Planting Dates & Crop Timing in {{ state.name }}</h1>

  {% set hero = (state.content and state.content.hero) or {} %}
  {% set ledeFromHeroNote = (hero and hero.note and (not hero.lede)) %}

  {# Optional hero notes (avoid duplicating hero.note if it was used as the lede) #}
  {% if hero %}
    {% set showHeroNote = (hero.note and (not ledeFromHeroNote)) %}
    {% if showHeroNote or hero.extraNote %}
      <div class="callout" style="margin-top:0.75rem;">
        {% if showHeroNote %}
          <p>{{ hero.note }}</p>
        {% endif %}
        {% if hero.extraNote %}
          <p>{{ hero.extraNote }}</p>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
    {% endif %}
  {% endif %}

  {% if state.season and state.season.frost and state.season.frost.spring and state.season.frost.fall %}
    <p class="lede">
      In a typical year, <strong>the growing season in {{ state.name }} runs roughly from
      {{ state.season.frost.spring.p50 | mmddLong }}
      through
      {{ state.season.frost.fall.p50 | mmddLong }}</strong>{% if state.season.derived and state.season.derived.frostFreeDays_p50 %} <strong>— about {{ state.season.derived.frostFreeDays_p50 }} frost-free days</strong> for most locations{% endif %}.
      Knowing that window helps clarify what typically succeeds, what can be a stretch, and how to time planting across the season.
    </p>
  {% endif %}

  {% set lede =
  (hero and hero.lede)
    or (ledeFromHeroNote and hero.note)
or ("This page shows what typically works in " + state.name + " in a normal year — what reliably finishes, what can be tight, and how timing decisions shape results across the season.")%}

<p class="lede">{{ lede }}</p>

</header>
{% include "region/modules/quick-planning-reference.njk" %}

{% include "region/modules/season-boundaries.njk" %}

{% include "region/modules/remaining-gdd.njk" %}

{# Optional one-off details: src/_includes/region/{{ state.key }}-details.njk #}
{% set detailsPath = "region/" + state.key + "-details.njk" %}
{% include detailsPath ignore missing %}
